Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.50,0:01:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,大戶愛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.46,0:01:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你在這種地方幹什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.76,0:01:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,散步
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.39,0:01:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,這麼晚了？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.31,0:01:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,這是夢？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.18,0:01:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,夢不好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.02,0:01:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,現實才更好？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.40,0:01:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,第一次免費
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.15,0:01:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,下次把錢包帶來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.32,0:01:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,多少錢？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.41,0:01:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,不用擔心  你肯定喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.37,0:01:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,畢竟這扭蛋很特別
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.62,0:01:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,特別？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.08,0:01:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,裡面裝著你想要的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.37,0:01:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我並沒有什麼想要的東西…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.47,0:02:01.43,Default,,0,0,0,,別騙人了  當然有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.36,0:02:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,那就是朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.30,0:02:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,那不是夢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.68,0:02:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,是不是該冷藏起來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.06,0:02:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,但要是還活著  是不是應該保溫才對
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.73,0:02:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,好硬
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.11,0:02:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,啊  說不定會把它煮熟了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.28,0:02:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,,它能打破嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.45,0:03:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,不如說  我可以打破它嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.88,0:03:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我去把包放下  你們先走
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.63,0:03:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,老地方？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.55,0:03:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.59,0:03:17.47,Default,,0,0,0,,愛！老師來囉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.51,0:03:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,大戶媽媽  不用勉強叫她起來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.18,0:03:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是來送這週的講義的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.98,0:03:25.64,Top,,0,0,0,,真是不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.64,0:03:27.27,Top,,0,0,0,,總是麻煩你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.27,0:03:28.90,Top,,0,0,0,,沒有沒有  不敢當
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.90,0:03:32.40,Top,,0,0,0,,我只是回家路上來看看罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.44,0:03:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,裡面是什麼呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.82,0:03:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,明天再到那裡去看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.09,0:03:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我出門了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.35,0:04:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,欸？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.94,0:04:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.91,0:04:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼我會在學校裡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.16,0:04:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你做的太過火了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.04,0:04:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,不搞大點她不懂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.29,0:04:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,欸…  那就再多加點
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.71,0:04:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,哦？你還說是我做得過火呢  你個魔鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.13,0:04:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,給在學校的各位提問：
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.10,0:04:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,要是班上有人被欺凌該怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.10,0:04:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯！正確答案當然是視而不見
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.25,0:05:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,大戶愛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.76,0:05:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,打破蛋  把蛋打破
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.51,0:05:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,蛋？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.47,0:05:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,就是奇妙蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.31,0:05:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你是說這個？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.60,0:05:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,快點打破它
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.73,0:05:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,但是這很硬  我打不破
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.52,0:05:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,快點打破！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.48,0:05:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,打破！打破它！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.28,0:05:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,吵死了！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.45,0:05:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你這不是做得挺好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.49,0:06:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的  為什麼要在這種地方打破啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.33,0:06:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你要是完事了  就出去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.13,0:06:39.09,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.80,0:06:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,也不需要用這種口氣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.38,0:06:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,高高在上讓人火大
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.47,0:06:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,用普通的語氣不就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.81,0:06:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,雖說我也應聲了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.37,0:07:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,站起來！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.16,0:07:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.24,0:07:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,要跑囉！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.12,0:07:11.29,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.92,0:07:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,那是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.46,0:07:24.88,Default,,800,0,0,,那個… 啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.01,0:07:24.88,Default,,0,800,0,,要快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.56,0:07:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,那是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.39,0:07:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.52,0:07:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,他們就是「視而不見」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.48,0:07:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.61,0:07:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.12,0:07:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,站起來！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.78,0:07:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,這邊這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.08,0:07:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.22,0:08:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡是肝臟？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.76,0:08:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,這不要緊吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.39,0:08:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,要走了！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.79,0:08:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,趕快趕快！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.50,0:08:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,,這是夢  一場噩夢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.47,0:08:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,給我看看你的傷口
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.84,0:08:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,欸？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.68,0:08:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,快點
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.97,0:08:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.43,0:09:00.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我的傷口不會消失
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.48,0:09:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,對你來說這是個夢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.36,0:09:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,但對我來說這是現實
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.82,0:09:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,總之  在打鈴之前我們要一直跑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.20,0:09:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,沒什麼可怕的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.32,0:09:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,它們只追我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.20,0:09:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,再說了你在這個世界是不死身
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.12,0:09:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,只要你的眼睛和心臟沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.04,0:09:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,那還叫不死身嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.46,0:09:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,說得也是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.63,0:09:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,討厭  為什麼會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.88,0:09:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,因為你買了蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.72,0:09:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我沒買
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.76,0:09:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,說是第一個免費
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.01,0:09:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,是嗎  沒什麼比免費更貴了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.18,0:09:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,這不好笑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.43,0:09:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,所以你沒有朋友？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.14,0:09:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,不是沒有  是不需要
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.86,0:09:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,騙人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.36,0:09:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.82,0:09:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,那你就不會打破蛋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.11,0:09:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,沒什麼好害羞的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.41,0:09:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,因為我也沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.53,0:09:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,騙人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.37,0:09:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,,是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.49,0:10:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,不過表面朋友也是有的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.04,0:10:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,「是啊是啊」「我知道」「好可愛」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.62,0:10:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,只會這樣附和的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.21,0:10:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我沒有摯友
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.22,0:10:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,現在回想起來  摯友真的很重要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.51,0:10:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,男朋友會分手  但摯友是一輩子的事對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.72,0:10:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.73,0:10:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,,你有過男朋友？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.39,0:10:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.52,0:10:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我先問的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.86,0:10:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,那我們「一二」一起說？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.40,0:10:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.24,0:10:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,一二
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.78,0:10:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你耍賴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.91,0:10:39.41,Default,,0,0,0,,你不也是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.70,0:10:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.08,0:10:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.54,0:10:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.26,0:11:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.68,0:11:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼要道歉？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.06,0:11:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,錯的是它們
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.31,0:11:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.19,0:11:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,真的  它們不來追我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.58,0:11:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,不來追我…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.81,0:12:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,小糸？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.48,0:12:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我叫長瀨小糸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.70,0:12:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,讓我們好好相處吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.16,0:12:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,那長瀨同學就坐大戶同學的旁邊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.91,0:12:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.56,0:13:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我們一起回家吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.56,0:13:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,欸？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.77,0:13:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,「欸」是什麼反應啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.02,0:13:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,太傷人了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.61,0:13:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡這麼清靜  是個好地方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.12,0:13:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你在做什麼呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.91,0:13:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,玩遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.41,0:13:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你喜歡遊戲？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.70,0:13:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,普普通通
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.83,0:13:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼遊戲？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.09,0:13:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,大戶同學？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.88,0:13:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,那…那個
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.97,0:13:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你和我在一起不太好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.60,0:13:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.06,0:13:48.31,Default,,0,0,0,,因為我是醜女
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.85,0:13:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.48,0:13:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,一點都不醜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.77,0:13:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,眼睛又大又圓
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.23,0:13:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你的髮型？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.94,0:14:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼要遮住這邊？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.12,0:14:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你的傘呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.96,0:14:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,忘記了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.33,0:14:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,你的包呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.54,0:14:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,愛？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.75,0:14:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,忘記了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.21,0:14:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,發生了什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.47,0:14:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼都沒有！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.23,0:14:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,愛  你朋友來看你了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.32,0:14:41.61,Default,,0,0,0,,她不是我朋友  我沒有朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.58,0:14:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我把你忘記的東西送來了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.38,0:14:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.43,0:15:11.77,Default,,0,0,0,,雙眼虹膜顏色不一樣  這叫做異色瞳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.77,0:15:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,常見於貓和狗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.77,0:15:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,真是神秘
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.69,0:15:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我覺得沒必要藏起來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.24,0:15:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,要知道我因此受欺凌
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.62,0:15:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,一直以來都是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.13,0:15:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,很漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.02,0:15:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,和我做朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.82,0:16:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,做摯友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.19,0:16:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,不行嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.45,0:16:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,也不是不行…但是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.57,0:16:13.49,Default,,0,0,0,,但是？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.49,0:16:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,要是能做摯友  我很高興
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.46,0:16:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.29,0:16:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,是我的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.50,0:16:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,因為我辜負了你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.47,0:16:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,明明是我交到的第一個朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.44,0:16:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,小糸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.76,0:17:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,就差一點  就差一點就要打鈴了的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.31,0:17:17.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我忍不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.73,0:17:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,不要過來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.54,0:17:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,斑馬線  即使和人群一起過也很可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.37,0:17:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我不會再視而不見了！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.74,0:18:21.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我已經怒不可遏了！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.89,0:18:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我叫西城胡桃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.23,0:18:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,大戶愛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.69,0:18:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,愛… 該告別了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.82,0:18:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,欸？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.90,0:18:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,不要忘記我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.66,0:19:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,遺憾
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.83,0:19:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,得救的就只有你一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.45,0:19:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,但是你得打起精神來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.33,0:19:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你想把摯友找回來的話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.21,0:19:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,欸？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.59,0:19:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,有點溫暖
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.97,0:19:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,因為我保護了胡桃？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.35,0:19:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,喂  要是我保護更多的人  小糸就能復活嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.68,0:19:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,對吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.94,0:19:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,愛  來吃飯了！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.78,0:19:36.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.07,0:19:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,今天天氣特別好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.20,0:19:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,所以不要總是睡在床上了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.74,0:19:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我把洗的衣服晾起來了  下午幫忙收回來哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.12,0:19:49.04,Top,,0,0,0,,呀  都已經這麼晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.79,0:19:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,原來如此  我在那邊是不死身  但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.34,0:19:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,媽媽今天早上要開會  所以現在就得出門了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.05,0:19:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,午餐…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.93,0:20:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,到底怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.47,0:20:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道  我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.60,0:20:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,該不會是晚上溜出去在外面被捲入什麼事件…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.39,0:20:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,冷靜…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.90,0:20:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,小糸…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.00,0:20:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,你好啊  傷情怎麼樣了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.71,0:20:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,算是搞定了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.09,0:20:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,錢包呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.46,0:20:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,帶來了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.34,0:20:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,要保護多少人小糸才能復活？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.89,0:20:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,唯獨這件事  我沒辦法告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.93,0:20:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,如果同時保護多個人  那就會更快一點？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.39,0:20:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你可真是個貪婪的小笨蛋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.60,0:20:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,要是沒保護好  你也沒辦法得救
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.19,0:20:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,小糸！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.74,0:21:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,而且  敵人也不全是那麼容易對付
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.32,0:21:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,畢竟它們只是「視而不見」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.53,0:21:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,一群烏合之眾
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.55,0:21:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,胡桃怎麼樣了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.71,0:21:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,就像你的摯友一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.72,0:21:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,在某個世界裡變成了雕像
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.22,0:21:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,除非她的朋友去到那個世界  不然她就永遠那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.81,0:21:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,胡桃她也自殺了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.18,0:21:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,無可奉告
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.31,0:21:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,無可奉告
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.75,0:21:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,歡迎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.21,0:21:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,初次見面  我是大號
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.05,0:22:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,你左邊的是小號
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.01,0:22:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,喲
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.14,0:22:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,有別的客人先來了  你稍等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.26,0:22:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.23,0:22:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,欸  還有其他人嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.24,0:22:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,那孩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.16,0:22:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.58,0:22:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我們也一直很擔心…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.74,0:22:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,身材好厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.66,0:22:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你說的這個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.26,0:22:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,待續
